<p>When the system, shown in the diagram, is released from rest, the magnitude of the acceleration 
of each block is \(g/3\). The masses of the blocks are \(m\) and \(3m\), the radius of the pulley is \(r\). There is no slipping between the pulley and the light string that connects the blocks. Find the moment of inertia of the pulley.</p>

    <br/>
